summary: AN ORDINANCE authorizing easement and consent agreements with Snohomish County Public Utility District No. 1 (the "District") for use of the City of Seattle Skagit Transmission Line Right of Way in Snohomish County, Washington, for a 115,000 volt electric transmission system, guy wires and anchors, and ingress to and egress from the same. (P.M. \#'s 310619-4-301 and 310630-1-301)
